name: Guac-A-Mole: Ultimate Avocado Smash
summary: Embark on a vibrant mole-whacking adventure with 'Guac-A-Mole', where classic arcade meets immersive VR. Wield your virtual mallet across diverse, colorful landscapes filled with unique challenges and hidden surprises. Perfect your aim and timing to outsmart mischievous moles popping up from their hideouts. With increasing levels of difficulty, 'Guac-A-Mole' tests your strategy and precision, offering an engaging experience that keeps you on your toes.
